english.segment1: Artist: Third Day. Album: Offerings: A Worship Album. Song: Agnes Dei/Worthy
english.segment2: Alleluia, Alleluia. For our Lord God Almighty reigns. Alleluia, Alleluia. For our Lord God Almighty reigns
english.segment3: Holy, Holy. Are You Lord God Almighty. Worthy is the Lamb. Worthy is the Lamb. You are Holy. Holy. Are You Lord God Almighty. Worthy Is the Lamb. Worthy Is the Lamb. Amen
english.segment4: Holy, You are holy. King of kings, Lord of lords. You are holy. Holy, you are holy. King of kings, Lord of lords. I worship you
